divs: Sighting DetailsClimbing Cathedral Rock in Sedona I took lots of photos on this clear day. When I got home and opened the photos and enlarged the attached picture and I noticed 2 silver objects and 4 dark objects in some sort of pattern in the sky. When I looked at the other photos I took they were not there.
